title SIE - Systemic Processes End-to-End (Definition Plane internal, full control coverage) - v1

autonumber

' ============================================================
' PARTICIPANTS (Definition Plane internal)
' - No lifelines for receptors/effectors/state objects/events/BehavioralRule/controls
' - Events are represented only as messages to/from the Bus
' - Each control is a self-call on its owning controller lifeline
' ============================================================

box "Definition Plane" #E8F4E8
  participant "Event Bus" as Bus
  participant "Operator\n(owns Homeostasis)" as Operator
  participant "Supervisor\n(owns Adaptation)" as Supervisor
  participant "Governor\n(owns Emergence + Coherence)" as Governor
end box

actor "Decision Owner\n(human input)" as DecisionOwner

note over Bus
  **Detailed, instance-aligned sequences (same folder):**
  - governance-process/sie-homeostasis-sequence-v1.puml
  - governance-process/sie-adaptation-sequence-v1.puml
  - governance-process/sie-coherence-check-feasibility-sequence-v1.puml
  - governance-process/sie-coherence-admission-sequence-v1.puml
  - governance-process/sie-emergence-sequence-v1.puml

  This diagram is *Definition-plane internal*:
  - Evidence originates outside Definition plane and arrives as Bus deliveries.
  - Actuation executes outside Definition plane; outcomes return as evidence deliveries.
end note

note over Bus, Governor
  **Closed-loop boundary (definition-centric):**
  - Evidence: State → Description → (Bus delivers into Definition)
  - Definition: controllers evolve definitions + emit actuation intents
  - Outcomes: observed outside Definition plane → re-enter as new evidence
end note

' ============================================================
' END-TO-END FLOW (includes ALL controls)
' ============================================================

== 0) Triggers (inbound to Definition plane) ==
note over Bus
  Typical inbound deliveries include:
  - ControlIntentEvent (drives Homeostasis phases)
  - MismatchAssessmentEvent (drives Adaptation)
  - CoherenceRequestEvent (CHECK / FEASIBILITY / ADMISSION)
  - EmergenceTriggerEvent
  - ActuationFeedbackEvent (observed outside Definition plane)
end note

== 1) Homeostasis (Operator; BRC-HOM-001..003) ==
group Trigger
  Bus -> Operator : deliver ControlIntentEvent
end

alt ControlIntentEvent.phase == "ASSESS"
  loop while ControlIntentEvent.repeatAssessment == true
    Operator -> Operator : BRC-HOM-001 Assess Drift / Stability
    Operator -> Bus : publish RuleExecutionRequestEvent
  end
else ControlIntentEvent.phase == "ACTUATE"
  loop while ControlIntentEvent.repeatActuation == true
    Operator -> Operator : BRC-HOM-002 Modify State (Actuation)
    Operator -> Bus : publish ActuationControlEvent

    ... feedback arrives via Bus (produced outside Definition plane) ...
    Bus -> Operator : deliver ActuationFeedbackEvent
  end
else ControlIntentEvent.phase == "RETENTION"
  Operator -> Operator : BRC-HOM-003 Enforce Evidence Retention
  Operator -> Bus : publish RetentionAppliedEvent
else (phase not applicable)
  note over Operator
    No Homeostasis control applies.
  end note
end

== 2) Adaptation (Supervisor; BRC-ADP-001..002) ==
group Trigger
  Bus -> Supervisor : deliver MismatchAssessmentEvent
end

alt MismatchAssessmentEvent.diagnosisNeeded == true
  loop while MismatchAssessmentEvent.repeatDiagnosis == true
    Supervisor -> Supervisor : BRC-ADP-001 Diagnose Control Performance
    Supervisor -> Bus : publish BehavioralRuleCandidateEvent
  end
else (no diagnosis)
  note over Supervisor
    BRC-ADP-001 not applicable.
  end note
end

alt MismatchAssessmentEvent.candidateRuleStatus == "PUBLISHED"
  loop while MismatchAssessmentEvent.waitingForRealization == true
    Supervisor -> Supervisor : BRC-ADP-002 Provision New Operator Definition
    Supervisor -> Bus : publish OperatorProvisioningEvent
    Bus -> Operator : deliver OperatorProvisioningEvent
  end
else (candidate not published)
  note over Supervisor
    BRC-ADP-002 not applicable.
  end note
end

== 3) Coherence (Governor; BRC-COH-001..018) ==
group CHECK + FEASIBILITY
  Bus -> Governor : deliver CoherenceRequestEvent(phase=CHECK)

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-001 Select Check Set
  Governor -> Bus : publish CoherenceCheckPlanEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-002 Request Evidence Grounding
  Governor -> Bus : publish EvidenceGroundingRequestEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-003 Request Supervisor Checks
  Governor -> Bus : publish SupervisorCheckRequestEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-004 Aggregate Reports
  Governor -> Bus : publish CoherenceReportEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-005 Detect Circular Dependency
  Governor -> Bus : publish IncoherenceDetectedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-006 Auto-Resolve Stale Reference
  Governor -> Bus : publish ResolutionProposedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-007 Apply Graph Sync
  Governor -> Bus : publish GraphSyncAppliedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-008 Auto-Define Missing Sensor
  Governor -> Bus : publish SensorAutoDefinedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-009 Deprecate Unused Sensor
  Governor -> Bus : publish SensorDeprecatedEvent

  Bus -> Governor : deliver CoherenceRequestEvent(phase=FEASIBILITY)
  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-010 Request Feasibility Checks
  Governor -> Bus : publish FeasibilityAssessmentRequestedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-011 Aggregate Feasibility Reports
  Governor -> Bus : publish FeasibilityAggregatedEvent
end

group ADMISSION (BRC-COH-012..018; reuses 005..009)
  Bus -> Governor : deliver CoherenceRequestEvent(phase=ADMISSION)

  note over Governor
    In ADMISSION phase, Coherence also executes controls 005..009 before 012..018.
    They are shown above to avoid duplication.
  end note

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-012 Validate DefinitionBundle
  Governor -> Bus : publish DefinitionBundleValidationReportEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-013 Policy & Rule Static Analysis
  Governor -> Bus : publish PolicyAndRuleStaticAnalysisReportEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-014 Constraint Satisfiability Checking
  Governor -> Bus : publish ConstraintSatisfiabilityReportEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-015 Execute Definition Test Suite
  Governor -> Bus : publish DefinitionTestSuiteReportEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-016 Admission Gate Decision
  Governor -> Bus : publish AdmissionGateDecisionEvent

  alt AdmissionGateDecisionEvent.outcome == "PASS"
    note over Governor
      Admission gate computed PASS.
    end note
  else AdmissionGateDecisionEvent.outcome == "FAIL"
    note over Governor
      Admission gate computed FAIL.
    end note
  else AdmissionGateDecisionEvent.outcome == "NEEDS_REVIEW"
    Governor -> DecisionOwner : manual review required
  end

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-017 Record Governance Decision
  Governor -> Bus : publish GovernanceDecisionRecordedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-COH-018 Controlled Activation Plan
  Governor -> Bus : publish ControlledActivationPlanEvent
end

== 4) Emergence (Governor; BRC-EMG-001..007) ==
group Trigger
  Bus -> Governor : deliver EmergenceTriggerEvent
end

Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-001 Open Emergence Case
Governor -> Bus : publish EmergenceCaseOpenedEvent

alt EmergenceTriggerEvent.proposal.confidence >= 0.7
  Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-004 Auto-Approve High Confidence
  Governor -> Bus : publish EmergenceApprovedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-003 Publish New Definitions
  Governor -> Bus : publish DefinitionChangedEvent

  Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-006 Deprecate Before Create
  Governor -> Bus : publish PrimitiveDeprecateAndCreateEvent
else EmergenceTriggerEvent.proposal.confidence < 0.7
  loop while DecisionResponseEvent.received == false
    Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-002 Request Decision
    Governor -> Bus : publish DecisionRequestEvent
    Bus -> DecisionOwner : deliver DecisionRequestEvent

    Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-005 Escalate Low Confidence
    Governor -> Bus : publish ApprovalRequiredEvent
    Bus -> DecisionOwner : deliver ApprovalRequiredEvent

    DecisionOwner -> Bus : publish DecisionResponseEvent
    Bus -> Governor : deliver DecisionResponseEvent
  end

  alt DecisionResponseEvent.outcome == "APPROVED"
    Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-003 Publish New Definitions
    Governor -> Bus : publish DefinitionChangedEvent

    Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-006 Deprecate Before Create
    Governor -> Bus : publish PrimitiveDeprecateAndCreateEvent
  else (not approved)
    note over Governor
      Decision did not approve; no definition publication.
    end note
  end
end

Governor -> Governor : BRC-EMG-007 Close Emergence Case
Governor -> Bus : publish EmergenceCaseClosedEvent

== 5) Close the loop ==
note over Bus
  Outcomes are observed outside Definition plane and re-enter as evidence deliveries
  (e.g., MismatchAssessmentEvent, ActuationFeedbackEvent).
end note

@enduml
